{
  "stem": "14810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to get up 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The kapos came in with sticks and bats, and they used to-- and they used to club us, beat us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you could see them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They had so much fun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I just-- it had only one door, and here you've got so many hundreds of people and everybody was trying to run, get to be first, get out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they stood there by the door, about four of them, and with the sticks and bats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was-- I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you could see it every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It came to the point I didn't take off my clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I just slept in my clothes and didn't take off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So when they came, 5 o'clock, I wanted to be the first so I wouldn't get clobbered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that was daily routine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was daily routine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then had to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They had-- in the barracks was no sanitation whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And here you got 600 to 700 people and 9 o'clock was curfew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You couldn't go in, and you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And here, after all, we were human, and many of us needed to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So most of them relieved themselves in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then when they find out-- the stench was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then they came, and if they found out somebody, you know, relieved themselves, they clobbered them to death-- literally killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They called them schwein, you schweinhunde.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Those people couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And that was about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And all I did-- we had to stay outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They had nothing to do for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But they just tortured us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They had quarries with stones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I remember big, heavy stones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So we had to pick up the stones, carry them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
